&lt;li&gt;Identify, recommend, and implement process improvements to strengthen financial controls, reduce risk, and improve scalability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to ad hoc projects and cross-functional initiatives as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIRED EXPERIENCE AND SKILLS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ACA / ACCA (or equivalent) qualified&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in financial accounting/financial control, including balance sheet ownership, reconciliations, journals, and statutory reporting support&lt;/li&gt;
