&lt;p data-start=&quot;142&quot; data-end=&quot;492&quot;&gt;Maven is a market-leading, employee-owned proprietary trading firm deploying internal capital across discretionary, systematic, and market-making strategies. We differentiate ourselves by exclusively managing our own capital, delivering exceptional returns on equity since inception, and preserving an entrepreneurial, highly collaborative culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an outstanding Equity Investment Analyst to join our Hong Kong team. This individual will play an important role is supporting portfolio managers in equity research and investment decision making focused on Japan listed Companies.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
