&lt;li&gt;Language capability: excellent verbal and written communication skills in English is required. Native proficiency in Japanese is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and with a minimum amount of supervision, demonstrating a high degree of initiative, judgement, and professionalism&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
