&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE: &lt;/strong&gt;We are looking for ambitious and proactive Options Market Makers with a proven profit / risk management history to be a part of our expanding trading desk. The eligible candidate must be willing to trade a variety of instruments to help expand the expansion of our US office in Chicago.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
