&lt;li&gt;Successful track record of proven P&amp;amp;L and market share&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good understanding of trading systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding numerical and analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with automated options trading strategies and an interest in their development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive interest in improving existing trading strategies and identifying new opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to take a high level of responsibility in an expanding, highly successful firm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
