&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Core Infrastructure team&lt;/strong&gt; is a diverse group of technologists, who focus on continuously improving the end-to-end resiliency, scalability, visibility, usability, and supportability of Maven&#39;s technology systems.&lt;/p&gt;
